import React from "react";

import {
  ServicesContainer,
  ServicesH1,
  ServicesCard,
  ServicesH2,
  ServicesIcon,
  ServicesP,
  ServicesWrapper,
} from "./ServicesElements";

const Services = () => {
  return (
    <>
      <ServicesContainer id="discover">
        <ServicesH1>Our Services</ServicesH1>
        <ServicesWrapper>
          <ServicesCard>
            <ServicesIcon src="/images/savings.svg" />
            <ServicesH2>Reduce Expenses</ServicesH2>
            <ServicesP>Save money by finding your weakspots.</ServicesP>
          </ServicesCard>
          <ServicesCard>
            <ServicesIcon src="/images/investing.svg" />
            <ServicesH2>No Fees</ServicesH2>
            <ServicesP>Premium benefits</ServicesP>
          </ServicesCard>
          <ServicesCard>
            <ServicesIcon src="/images/signup.svg" />
            <ServicesH2>Unlock</ServicesH2>
            <ServicesP>Your true desires</ServicesP>
          </ServicesCard>
        </ServicesWrapper>
      </ServicesContainer>
    </>
  );
};

export default Services;
